TIC TAC TOE JAVA GAME

DESCRIPTION
A simple console-based Tic Tac Toe game written in Java.

QUICK START
1. Compile: javac TicTacToe.java
2. Run: java TicTacToe

HOW TO PLAY
- Two players take turns (X and O)
- Enter moves as: row column
- Use numbers 0-2 for positions
- Example: "1 1" for center position

BOARD LAYOUT
(0,0) | (0,1) | (0,2)
(1,0) | (1,1) | (1,2)
(2,0) | (2,1) | (2,2)

FEATURES
- Win detection
- Tie game handling
- Input validation
- Clean console display

CONTROLS
- Enter row (0-2)
- Enter column (0-2)
- Follow on-screen prompts

TROUBLESHOOTING
- Ensure Java is installed
- Run in terminal/command prompt
- Use numbers 0-2 only
